---
// Blog component - shows blog entries list
---

<div id="blog-modal" class="blog-modal">
  <div class="blog-content">
    <h2>Blog</h2>
    <div class="blog-list">
      <article class="blog-entry">
        <h3>Building Interactive Space Animations with CSS</h3>
        <p class="blog-date">December 20, 2025</p>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          Exploring how to create mesmerizing star field animations using pure CSS transforms and keyframes. 
          Learn the techniques behind creating smooth, performant space-themed backgrounds.
        </p>
      </article>
      
      <article class="blog-entry">
        <h3>The Magic of Component-Based Architecture</h3>
        <p class="blog-date">December 15, 2025</p>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          Diving deep into modern web development patterns and how breaking down complex UIs into 
          reusable components can transform your development workflow.
        </p>
      </article>
      
      <article class="blog-entry">
        <h3>From Stars to Text: Advanced Animation Sequences</h3>
        <p class="blog-date">December 10, 2025</p>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          A technical breakdown of creating complex animation sequences that tell a story. 
          How to coordinate multiple elements to create seamless visual narratives.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-entry">
        <h3>Responsive Design in the Age of Flexible Layouts</h3>
        <p class="blog-date">December 5, 2025</p>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          Mastering modern CSS Grid and Flexbox techniques to create layouts that adapt beautifully 
          across all device sizes. Tips for building truly responsive experiences.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-entry">
        <h3>Performance Optimization: Making the Web Faster</h3>
        <p class="blog-date">November 28, 2025</p>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          Essential strategies for optimizing web performance, from lazy loading images to 
          efficient JavaScript bundling. Learn how to make your sites lightning fast.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-entry">
        <h3>The Art of Minimalist Web Design</h3>
        <p class="blog-date">November 22, 2025</p>
        <p class="blog-excerpt">
          Exploring the principles of clean, minimal design and how less can truly be more. 
          Creating impactful user experiences through thoughtful simplicity and purposeful whitespace.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .blog-modal {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 15;
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease;
  }

  .blog-modal.show {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  .blog-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    width: 90%;
    max-height: 70vh;
    color: white;
    font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Arial Nova', 'Nimbus Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
    transform: scale(1);
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding-right: 8px;
  }

  .blog-content::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 4px;
  }

  .blog-content::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .blog-content::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .blog-content::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 32px 0;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .blog-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .blog-entry {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .blog-entry:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .blog-entry h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .blog-date {
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .blog-excerpt {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-content {
      margin: 20px;
      max-height: 60vh;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .blog-list {
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .blog-entry h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .blog-excerpt {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }
</style>